  "monster": {
    "title": "Saxafra.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Saxafra has a fat light green body with dragonfly wings and an ominous eye at the end of a thin stalk. It is surrounded by a weird haze.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 189     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++++ +   </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: ++++ +    </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: +..     </lightgrey><darkgrey>   rC: ...      </darkgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: ∞        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\n\n\nYou have about 67% to hit with your claws.\nIt has about 53% to hit you.\n\nAttack  Max Damage  \nHit     46          \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to steam and miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can fly.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.\n\nIt is currently targeting Letoel's ghost.\n\nThis monster has been temporarily summoned to this location. If angered it will immediately vanish, yielding no experience or items; it is incapable of using stairs.",
    "quote": "",
    "status": "<white>Silenced:<lightgrey>\n   This creature is engulfed in a field of unnatural silence, preventing any\n   noise it might make, including the vocalisations required for many creatures\n   to cast spells.\n\n<white>Radiating silence:<lightgrey>\n   This creature is surrounded by a field of unnatural silence which eliminates\n   all noise made within it as well as preventing the vocalisations required for\n   many creatures (including you) to read scrolls, cast spells, or invoke divine\n   aid.\n   \n   If this effect was caused by a spell, the radius of the field will shrink\n   over time.\n\n<white>Unaffected by silence:<lightgrey>\n   Despite being engulfed in unnatural silence, this creature's magic does not\n   require vocalisations and thus is unaffected.\n\n",
